==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: The big eye stares at the small eye.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: dà yăn dèng xĭao yăn

===Idiom===
'''[[大]][[眼]][[瞪]][[小]][[眼]]'''

# Two people staring at each other, without knowing what to do.

